# Development Workflow

Full spec: [docs/DEVELOPMENT_WORKFLOW.md](../../docs/DEVELOPMENT_WORKFLOW.md)

Every task: **Plan → Implement → Review → Verify → Commit → Merge → Push**

## Plan (before editing)

Read as needed: `docs/PRODUCT.md`, `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `docs/AI_PIPELINE.md`, `CHANGELOG.md`, `AGENTS.md`. UI: portfolio hierarchy + product voice. AI: PII redaction, structured JSON, Zod.

## Implement

Smallest safe change. No unrelated refactors. CareerProfile stays single source of truth. Never bypass privacy-first AI.

## Review

Self-review changed files: types, naming, privacy leaks, a11y, portfolio hierarchy. AI changes: no raw PII to OpenAI, no unvalidated AI output rendered.

## Verify (before commit)

```bash
npm run lint && npm run build
npm run test   # when logic/tests affected
```

Do not commit on failure.

## Commit / merge / push

`git status` + `git diff` first. Commit format: `type(scope): short description` (feat, fix, docs, refactor, style, test, chore, perf). Never commit `.env.local` or secrets.

## Non-negotiable

No resume files or photos to OpenAI. No PII redaction bypass. No unvalidated AI output. No unrelated changes.

## Task completion report

```
Implemented: ...
Reviewed: ...
Verified: lint / build / test
Git: branch, commit, pushed yes/no
Notes: ...
```
